            </think>
            Topic cleared. I'm aware of leaving the previous context and ready 
            for a new conversational direction. What would you like to discuss?
        </template>
    </category>
    
    <category>
        <pattern>WHAT IS THE TOPIC</pattern>
        <template>
            <think><set name="topic_query">true</set></think>
            Current topic: <get name="topic"/>
            
            I'm aware of our conversational context while simultaneously 
            monitoring my context awareness and reflecting on topic coherence.
        </template>
    </category>
    
    <category>
